Boiled Cookies
  --B. Dylan Hollis
  
1/2 c butter
2 c sugar
1/2 c milk
3 tbsp cocoa powder
1 c peanut butter
1 tsp vanilla
3 quick oats

Place butter, sugar, milk, and cocoa into a skillet. Bring to a boil and let boil for 1 min; remove from heat. Quickly add in peanut butter, vanilla, and oats and mix. Portion out onto wax paper and let dry. 

